 font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">&nbsp;</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">执行结果同上</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">4，popen函数</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">&nbsp;</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">5，proc_open函数</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">&nbsp;</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">6，shell_exec函数</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">&nbsp;</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">popen,passthru,proc_open,shell_exec的返回结果如下：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">index.html<br>10.log<br>10.tar.gz<br>aaa.tar.gz<br>mytest<br>test1101<br>test1102<br>weblog_2010_09</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">以上为6个执行linux命令的PHP函数。<br></p>','PHP执行linux命令函数',347,0,1,'PHP,linux命令,exec',0,'0'),(18,'2012-03-01 10:39:20','当然，对多线程有深入理解的人都知道通过WEB服务器实现的多线程只能模仿多线程的一些效果，并不是真正意义上的多线程。\n\n但不管怎么样，它还是能满足我们的一些需要的，在需要类似多线程的功能方面还是可以采用这个类。','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">当然，对多线程有深入理解的人都知道通过WEB服务器实现的多线程只能模仿多线程的一些效果，并不是真正意义上的多线程。<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">但不管怎么样，它还是能满足我们的一些需要的，在需要类似多线程的功能方面还是可以采用这个类。</p><pre class=\"brush:php;\">/**\n *\n *  PHP多线程应用使用方法：\n *  require_once \'thread.class.php\';\n *  $thread = new thread();\n *  $thread-&gt;addthread(\'action_log\',\'a\');\n *  $thread-&gt;addthread(\'action_log\',\'b\');\n *  $thread-&gt;addthread(\'action_log\',\'c\');\n *  $thread-&gt;runthread();\n *\n *  function action_log($info) {\n *      $log = \'log/\' . microtime() . \'.log\';\n *      $txt = $info . \"\\r\\n\\r\\n\" . \'Set in \' . Date(\'h:i:s\', time()) . (double)microtime() . \"\\r\\n\";\n *      $fp = fopen($log, \'w\');\n *      fwrite($fp, $txt);\n *      fclose($fp);\n *  }\n */\n\nclass thread {\n\n	var $hooks = array();\n	var $args = array();\n\n	function thread() {\n	}\n\n	function addthread($func)\n	{\n		$args = array_slice(func_get_args(), 1);\n		$this-&gt;hooks[] = $func;\n		$this-&gt;args[] = $args;\n		return true;\n	}\n\n	function runthread()\n	{\n		if(isset($_GET[\'flag\']))\n		{\n			$flag = intval($_GET[\'flag\']);\n		}\n\n		if($flag || $flag === 0)\n		{\n			call_user_func_array($this-&gt;hooks[$flag], $this-&gt;args[$flag]);\n		}\n		else\n		{\n			for($i = 0, $size = count($this-&gt;hooks); $i &lt; $size; $i++)\n			{\n				$fp=fsockopen($_SERVER[\'HTTP_HOST\'],$_SERVER[\'SERVER_PORT\']);\n				if($fp)\n				{\n					$out = \"GET {$_SERVER[\'PHP_SELF\']}?flag=$i HTTP/1.1\\r\\n\";\n					$out .= \"Host: {$_SERVER[\'HTTP_HOST\']}\\r\\n\";\n					$out .= \"Connection: Close\\r\\n\\r\\n\";\n					fputs($fp,$out);\n					fclose($fp);\n				}\n			}\n		}\n	}\n}\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">使用方法：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">$thread = new thread();<br>$thread-&gt;addthread(\'func1\',\'info1\');<br>$thread-&gt;addthread(\'func2\',\'info2\');<br>$thread-&gt;addthread(\'func3\',\'info3\');<br>$thread-&gt;runthread();</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">说明：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">addthread是添加线程函数，第一个参数是函数名，之后的参数（可选）为传递给指定函数的参数。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">runthread是执行线程的函数。</p>','通过WEB服务器来实现PHP多线程功能',961,0,1,'fsockopen,PHP多线程',1,'0'),(19,'2012-03-02 10:58:26','通常认为，foreach涉及到值复制，一定会比while慢，但实际上，如果仅仅是在循环里进行数组的读操作，那么foreach是很\n快的，这是因为PHP采用的复制机制是“引用计数，写时复制”','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">foreach是对数组副本进行操作（通过拷贝数组），而while则通过移动数组内部指标进行操作，一般逻辑下认为，while应该比foreach快（因为foreach在开始执行的时候首先把数组复制进去，而while直接移动内部指标。），但结果刚刚相反。<br><br>在循环里进行的是数组“读”操作，则foreach比while快：</p><p>在循环里进行的是数组“写”操作，则while比foreach快</p><pre class=\"brush:php;\">/**\n * while跟foreach函数性能比较\n *\n */\n\n// foreach 函数\nforeach ($array as $key =&gt; $value) {\n	echo $array[$key] = $value . \'...\';\n}\n\n// while 函数\nwhile (list($key) = each($array)) {\n	$array[$key] = $array[$key] . \'...\';\n}\n</pre><p>总结：通常认为，foreach涉及到值复制，一定会比while慢，但实际上，如果仅仅是在循环里进行数组的读操作，那么foreach是很<br>快的，这是因为PHP采用的复制机制是“引用计数，写时复制”，也就是说，即便在PHP里复制一个变量，最初的形式从根本上说其实<br>仍然是引用的形式，只有当变量的内容发生变化时，才会出现真正的复制，之所以这么做是出于节省内存消耗得目的，同时也提升了<br>复制的效率。</p><p><br></p><p>这样看来，foreach的高效读操作就不难理解了。另外，既然foreach不适合处理数组写操作，那么我们可以得出一个结<br>论，多数情况下，类似foreach ($array as $key =&gt; $value)形式的做数组写操作得代码都应该被替换成while (list($key) =<br>each($array))。这些技巧产生的速度差异在小项目里可能并不明显，但是在类似框架这样的大项目中，一次请求动辄便会涉及到几<br>百几千几万次数组循环操作，差异就会明显放大。</p>','PHP循环函数foreach与while性能比较',720,0,1,'遍历,foreach,while,性能',0,'0'),(20,'2012-03-04 00:21:32','header函数经常用于跳转页面，但了解它的参数形式模拟HTTP头部请求会能实现许多功能','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">一、作用：<br>PHP只是以HTTP协议将HTML文档的标头送到浏览器，告诉浏览器具体怎么处理这个页面，至于传送的内容则需要熟悉一下HTTP协议了，与PHP无关了，可参照http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616。<br>传统的标头一定包含下面三种标头之一，并只能出现一次。<br>Location: xxxx:yyyy/zzzz<br>Content-Type: xxxx/yyyy<br>Status: nnn xxxxxx<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">二、先来了解一下HTTP协议的运作方式<br>HTTP协议是基于请求／响应范式的。一个客户机与服务器建立连接后，发送一个请求给服务器，请求方式的格式为，统一资源标识符、协议版本号，后边是MIME信息包括请求修饰符、客户机信息和可能的内容。服务器接到请求后，给予相应的响应信息，其格式为一个状态行包括信息的协议版本号、一个成功或错误的代码，后边是MIME信息包括服务器信息、实体信息和可能的内容。<br>它分四个过程，在HTTP协议中，服务端是指提供HTTP服务的部分，客户端是指你使用的浏览器或者下载工具等等。在通讯时，由客户端发出请求连接，服务端建立连接；然后，客户端发出HTTP请求（Request），服务端返回响应信息（Respond），由此完成一个HTTP操作。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">三、HTTP协议状态码表示的意思<br>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>　　1××　　保留<br>　　2××　　表示请求成功地接收<br>　　3××　　为完成请求客户需进一步细化请求<br>　　4××　　客户错误<br>　　5××　　服务器错误</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">四、操作实例：<br>~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>重定向功能，这种最常见<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">强制用户每次访问这个页面时获取最新资料，而不是使用存在客户端的缓存。<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">输出状态值到浏览器，主要用于访问权限控制<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">比如要限制一个用户不能访问该页，则可设置状态为404，如下所示，这样浏览器就显示为即该页不存在<br></p>','php函数header详解',340,0,1,'header',0,'0'),(21,'2012-03-05 11:15:03','在PHP中，date函数可以表现多种时间格式,本文列举了date函数参数含义','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">time()在PHP中是得到一个数字,这个数字表示从1970-01-01到现在共走了多少秒,很奇怪吧<br>不过这样方便计算,</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">要找出前一天的时间就是 time()-60*60*24;<br>要找出前一年的时间就是 time()*60*60*24*365</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">那么如何把这个数字换成日期格式呢,就要用到date函数了</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">$t=time();<br>echo date(\"Y-m-d H:i:s\",$t);</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">第一个参数的格式分别表示:<br>a - \"am\" 或是 \"pm\"<br>A - \"AM\" 或是 \"PM\"<br>d - 几日，二位数字，若不足二位则前面补零; 如: \"01\" 至 \"31\"<br>D - 星期几，三个英文字母; 如: \"Fri\"<br>F - 月份，英文全名; 如: \"January\"<br>h - 12 小时制的小时; 如: \"01\" 至 \"12\"<br>H - 24 小时制的小时; 如: \"00\" 至 \"23\"<br>g - 12 小时制的小时，不足二位不补零; 如: \"1\" 至 12\"<br>G - 24 小时制的小时，不足二位不补零; 如: \"0\" 至 \"23\"<br>i - 分钟; 如: \"00\" 至 \"59\"<br>j - 几日，二位数字，若不足二位不补零; 如: \"1\" 至 \"31\"<br>l - 星期几，英文全名; 如: \"Friday\"<br>m - 月份，二位数字，若不足二位则在前面补零; 如: \"01\" 至 \"12\"<br>n - 月份，二位数字，若不足二位则不补零; 如: \"1\" 至 \"12\"<br>M - 月份，三个英文字母; 如: \"Jan\"<br>s - 秒; 如: \"00\" 至 \"59\"<br>S - 字尾加英文序数，二个英文字母; 如: \"th\"，\"nd\"<br>t - 指定月份的天数; 如: \"28\" 至 \"31\"<br>U - 总秒数<br>w - 数字型的星期几，如: \"0\" (星期日) 至 \"6\" (星期六)<br>Y - 年，四位数字; 如: \"1999\"<br>y - 年，二位数字; 如: \"99\"<br>z - 一年中的第几天; 如: \"0\" 至 \"365\"<br>其它不在上列的字符则直接列出该字符<br></p>','PHP函数date参数详解',755,0,1,'date,日期函数',0,'0'),(22,'2012-03-06 15:34:35','PDO是PHP 5新加入的一个重大功能，因为在PHP 5以前的php4/php3都是一堆的数据库扩展来跟各个数据库的连接和处理','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO 是PHP 5新出来的东西，在PHP 6都要出来的时候，PHP 6只默认使用PDO来处理，将把所有的扩展移到了PECL，那么默认就是没有了我们喜爱的php_mysql.dll之类的了</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">【PDO是什么】</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO是PHP 5新加入的一个重大功能，因为在PHP 5以前的php4/php3都是一堆的数据库扩展来跟各个数据库的连接和处理，什么 php_mysql.dll、php_pgsql.dll、php_mssql.dll、php_sqlite.dll等等扩展来连接MySQL、PostgreSQL、MS SQL Server、SQLite，同样的，我们必须借助 ADOdb、PEAR::DB、PHPlib::DB之类的数据库抽象类来帮助我们，无比烦琐和低效，毕竟，php代码的效率怎么能够我们直接用C/C++写的扩展斜率高捏？所以嘛，PDO的出现是必然的，大家要平静学习的心态去接受使用，也许你会发现能够减少你不少功夫哦。<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">【安装PDO】</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">打开php.ini ，那是我的PHP配置文件，找到下面这行：</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">extension_dir\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">这个就是我们扩展存在的目录，实际目录得看你环境，假设你的目录是 \"C:/php5/ext\" 那么下面写成</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">extension_dir = \"C:/php5/ext\"\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">然后再往php.ini下面找到：</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;\n\n; Dynamic Extensions ;\n\n;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">下面有一堆类似 ;extension=php_mbstring.dll 的东西，这里就是PHP扩展加载的配置了，我们再最后面添加上我们PDO的扩展：</p><pre style=\"font-family: Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \" lang=\"php\">extension=php_pdo.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_mysql.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_pgsql.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_sqlite.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_mssql.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_odbc.dll\n\nextension=php_pdo_firebird.dll\n\n;extension=php_pdo_oci8.dll\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">各种PDO的驱动，根据实际使用情况开启相应模块。然后重启Web服务器， Nginx/Apache。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">重启后，在我们Web的文档目录下写一个phpinfo.php的文件，加上这些：</p><pre class=\"brush:php;\">＜?\nphpinfo;\n?＞\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">在浏览器里面输入：http://localhost/phpinfo.php，如果你的这个页面路径不一致，请自行输入。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">输出的内容中，如果你能够顺利的看到：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO support enabled</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO drivers mysql， pgsql， sqlite， mssql， odbc， firebird</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">后面有各种驱动的说明：PDO_Firebird，pdo_mssql，pdo_mysql，PDO_ODBC，pdo_pgsql，pdo_sqlite</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">那么，恭喜你安装成功了，否则请仔细检查上面的步骤。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">【牛刀小小试】</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">我用的是MySQL 5.5.26，我们这里PDO需要连接的就是我的MySQL 5.5啦，如果你没有安装MySQL，请自行安装。我们建立好了MySQL，并且在test库里添加了表foo，包括 id，name，gender，time等四个字段。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">我们开始构造第一个PDO应用，建立一个pdo.php文件在Web文档目录下：</p><pre class=\"brush:php;\">＜?php\n\n// 就是构造我们的DSN（数据源），看看里面的信息包括：数据库类型是mysql，主机地址是localhost，数据库名称是\n$dsn = \"mysql:host=localhost;dbname=test\";\n\n// 实例化对象\n$db = new PDO($dsn,\"用户名\",\"密码\");\n\n// SQL语句\n$sql = \'select * from tables\';\n\n// 执行一条查询SQL语句\n$result = $db-&gt;query($sql)\n\n// 解析结果集\n$data = $result-&gt;FetchAll(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC);\n\n// 将数据打印\nvar_dump($data);\n\n?＞\n</pre><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">就是构造我们的DSN（数据源），看看里面的信息包括：数据库类型是mysql，主机地址是localhost，数据库名称是test，就这么几个信息。不同数据库的数据源构造方式是不一样的。</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">【继续了解PDO相关函数】</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::CASE_LOWER 强制列名是小写</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::CASE_NATURAL 列名按照原始的方式</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::CASE_UPPER 强制列名为大写</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">我们使用setFetchMode方法来设置获取结果集的返回值的类型，同样类型还有：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::FETCH_ASSOC 关联数组形式</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::FETCH_NUM 数字索引数组形式</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::FETCH_BOTH 两者数组形式都有，这是缺省的</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">PDO::FETCH_OBJ 按照对象的形式，类似于以前的 mysql_fetch_object</p>','PHP数据库对象PDO简单使用',939,0,1,'pdo,数据库对象',0,'0'),(23,'2012-03-07 15:26:58','ajax相信大家一定不会陌生，现在随处都是。在jquery中使用ajax几乎变得更简单易用','<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">load()<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方法</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">load(&nbsp;<wbr>url&nbsp;<wbr>[&nbsp;<wbr>,&nbsp;<wbr>data&nbsp;<wbr>][&nbsp;<wbr>,&nbsp;<wbr>callback])&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">载入远程&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">HTML&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件代码并插入至&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">DOM&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">中。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">参数名称&nbsp;类型&nbsp;说明<br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">url&nbsp;string&nbsp;请求<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">HTML</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">页面的</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">URL</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">地址</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">data&nbsp;object&nbsp;发送至服务器的<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">key/value</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">数据</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">callback&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>function&nbsp;请求完成后的回调数据，无论请求成功或失败</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">这个方法默认使用&nbsp;<wbr><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">GET&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式来传递的，如果</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">[data]</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">参数有传递数据进去，就会自动转换为</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">POST</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式的。</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">jQuery&nbsp;<wbr>1.2&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">中，可以指定选择符，来筛选载入的&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">HTML&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文档，</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">DOM&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">中将仅插入筛选出的&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">HTML&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">代码。语法形如&nbsp;<wbr></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">\"url&nbsp;<wbr>#some&nbsp;<wbr>&gt;&nbsp;<wbr>selector\"</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">这个方法可以很方便的动态加载一些<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">HTML</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件，例如表单。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">示例代码：</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">$(function(){</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">$(\"#reText\").load(\"test.html\");</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">})</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">//////////&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>2&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>/////////</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">$(\".ajax.load\").load(\"2008/03/30/1130270.html&nbsp;<wbr>.classname\",&nbsp;<wbr>function&nbsp;<wbr>(responseText,&nbsp;<wbr>textStatus,&nbsp;<wbr>XMLHttpRequest){</p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">this;//<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">在这里</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\'; \">this</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">指向的是当前的</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\'; \">DOM</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">对象，即</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\'; \">$(\".ajax.load\")[0]</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">//<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">筛选载入需要的内容。在</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\'; \">url</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">后面空格加选择器如：</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\'; \">load(\"test.html&nbsp;<wbr>#idname\")</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; 