-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Ajax</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">请求中，这种区别对用户是不可见的</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">2&nbsp;<wbr>GET<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式对传输的数据有大小限制（通常不能大于</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">2KB</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">），而是用</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">POST</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式传递比</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">GET</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式大得多（理论上不受限制）</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19px; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; \">3&nbsp;<wbr>GET<span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 宋体;\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方式请求的数据会被浏览器缓存起来，因此其他人就可以从浏览器的历史记录中读取到这些数据，在某些情况下，</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">GET</span><span data-mce-style=\"font